Package com.flipkart.DAO

Interface GymCentreInterfaceDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GymCentreDAO
    public interface GymCentreInterfaceDAO
    This interface defines the data access operations related to Gym Centre functionality. It includes methods for retrieving gym centres based on owner ID, centre ID, city, adding a new gym centre, managing approval status, and fetching pending gym centres.
